OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F427A1775772667
OL,3,CTwo teenagers seriously injured in e-
OL,4,Cbike crash
OL,6,FTwo 15-year-old boys are in a serious
OL,7,Fbut stable condition in hospital after
OL,8,Fa crash involving an e-bike in York.
OL,10,FOfficers were called to the scene of
OL,11,Fthe two-vehicle collision in the Acomb
OL,12,Farea of the city shortly after 9.30pm
OL,13,Fon Saturday (4 April).
OL,15,FNorth Yorkshire Police said the
OL,16,Fincident involved an adapted green
OL,17,FCalibre pedal cycle, which had been
OL,18,Fgiven electric assistance, and a white
OL,19,FFiat 500.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G1/3
