OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F427A1775772667
OL,3,CTwo teenagers seriously injured in e-
OL,4,Cbike crash
OL,6,FIt is believed the e-bike had
OL,7,Ftravelled down Ostman Road to the
OL,8,Fjunction of Danebury Drive, where it
OL,9,Fcollided with the Fiat, which had
OL,10,Ftravelled from Woodlea Avenue on to
OL,11,FDanebury Drive.
OL,13,FThe two teenage boys, from the York
OL,14,Farea, were taken to hospital with
OL,15,Fserious injuries where they remained
OL,16,Fyesterday in serious, but stable,
OL,17,Fconditions.
OL,19,FAn 18-year-old woman, the driver of
OL,20,Fthe Fiat, was uninjured, according to
OL,21,Fpolice.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G2/3
